'''''Hero, Return to Dawn in Mortality''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Delve into the Ruins of Time and reach the Scepter's core
# Awaken Phainon's heroic soul and become tomorrow's heroes together
# Free the obsession of Worldbearer and promise the salvation of the Trailblaze
# Irontomb has descended. Defeat it and extinguish the karmic flames of the Destruction

